          Flexible WiFi Connetion Options for Faster Speed / Longer Distance

          Previous page
          Next page

          Argus PT captures 4MP SHD videos, with a visual distance of up to 33 feet and a 105° wide field of view, day & night. The high-capacity rechargeable battery and WiFi connection make it completely wireless and ideal for outdoor use.

          Previous page

          1. Smarter Detection, More Accurate Alerts

            Send instant push notifications to you when the motion of a person or vehicle is detected.

          2. Focus on What Really Matters

            Customize the motion zone, deciding where to detect the motion and where not.

          3. Customizable PIR Schedule

            Set up PIR sensitivity and schedule for fewer false alarms and longer battery usage.

          4. Warn off the Intruder

            Once the camera detects suspicious motion, the custom siren will be activated in no time.

          5. Smart & Quick Playback

            Finding important moments is made much easier by the smart event filters and timeline.

          Next page

          Local Storage, No Hub Needed

          Stand-Alone with no hub needed. Local storage is available, and up to 128GB microSD card is supported (but not included). FAT32 format with Class 10 read/write speed is required. You can use on-camera smart features without subscription.

          Smart & Quick Playback

          Finding important moments is made much easier by the smart event filters and timeline and access and playback anytime and anywhere via Reolink APP/Client.

          Remote Live View

          Easy access from anywhere and live view anytime to know what's happening at your home or store via the free Reolink App/Client.

          Works with Smart Home Devices

          Ask your smart device to show you the camera's live feed simply via voice command. Actions speak louder than words? Words are enough.

          Capture the Dynamic Process

          It can speed up long processes like the whole construction process, sunrise, and sunset into minutes. Have fun viewing the changing world.

          Embraces Sunshine and Rain

          With a solar power supply and a waterproof body, the battery camera is ideal for outdoor use, rain or shine, hot or cold.

          How customer reviews and ratings work

          Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

          To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
